  <section>
    <h2>Basic Usage</h2>
    <p>The child <code>&lt;textarea data-grow&gt;</code> auto-resizes. The <code>[data-send]</code> button triggers submission.</p>
    <code-block language="html" show-lines label="Basic chat input">{{ basicCode | escape }}</code-block>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Inside a Form</h2>
    <p>As a form-associated element, <code>chat-input</code> participates in native <code>FormData</code>, form submit, and <code>reset()</code>.</p>
    <code-block language="html" show-lines label="Form-associated chat input">{{ formCode | escape }}</code-block>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Disabled State</h2>
    <p>Set <code>disabled</code> to prevent input. This also disables the send button and reduces opacity.</p>
    <code-block language="html" show-lines label="Disabled chat input">{{ disabledCode | escape }}</code-block>
  </section>

